        <mxCell id="h7UwSaR3J4pmbzhow-FZ-1" value="&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;Points to include&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;This is a list of things to mention:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Provide &lt;i&gt;introspective&amp;nbsp;&lt;/i&gt;awareness of issues.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;Facts pertaining&amp;nbsp;to social media use (fair representation: good + bad)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;Display &lt;u&gt;small&amp;nbsp;easy&lt;/u&gt;&amp;nbsp;steps to take, which are largely non-intrusive.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;Issues to ask reader to consider include:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;Time Spend&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;Value Gained&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;Ask how much comparison is caused by social media.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: initial;&quot;&gt;Ask if the comparison leads to a negative emotional experience.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Ask the reader about other people they know who have had positive experiences without social media.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Display alternative ways to spend time.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Ask the reader to come up with them.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Be concrete:&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;DON&#39;T claim that social media is the cause of all problems mentioned.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;DON&#39;T claim that removing social media fixes all problems mentioned.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;DON&#39;T claim that the only option is to remove social media.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Ask about:&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;If the time spend reflects the value gained&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;spacing=5;spacingTop=-20;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="16" y="74" width="463" height="374" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="h7UwSaR3J4pmbzhow-FZ-2" value="&lt;h1&gt;Keep in mind&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Stages of change are continuous, and people jump around:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Pre-contemplative&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Contemplation&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Determination&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Action (actually do a change)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Maintenance&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;spacing=5;spacingTop=-20;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
